{"tid":139971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞刀煞八鄉逞兇　撞車斬人縱火燒車釀4傷","createTime":"2017-03-02T00:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T14:21:06.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d26bef56d15aeb44acc2b5b8de28548883fba345","tid":139971,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T00:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/photo/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_01b.jpg?20170302073144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20170302073144&h=011b87b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中一名遇襲穿黑衣男子(左圖)，涉事2私家車焚毀，大批探員在場調查，現場遺下一件外套及一攤血漬。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<br />\n南亞刀煞夜襲八鄉，殺聲震天！現場八鄉青山公路潭尾段長春新村，凌晨1時許，一輛載乘4名本地男子的白色私家車，駛入長春新村沿小路入村時，一輛停泊在附近的神秘私家車，突然高速飛馳迎頭攔截白色私家車，2車迎頭相撞後，神秘私家車隨即跳下4名戴上飛虎頭套的南亞刀手，各人分持2呎長牛肉刀衝向白色私家車，並向司機位後座目標男乘客狂斬，車上3名男子制止時亦被斬傷，南亞幫傷人後再放火燒毀2車，分乘2輛接應私家車高速駛離現場。<br />\n<br />\n有街坊目睹事件，報警求助，消防員接報趕至開喉灌救，迅即將火救熄，惟2車已嚴重焚毀，消防員調查，認為火警有可疑，交警方處理。警方列為縱火及傷人案，現場地上遺下一件外套，一攤血漬，一把牛肉刀，一把短刀，而白色私家車後座位玻璃窗被扑碎，玻璃窗金屬框滿布刀痕，車廂內坐椅染滿血漬，警員亦在私家車內尋獲一罐燒毀助燃劑。<br />\n<br />\n事件中，私家車上4名本地男子同告受傷，其中27歲姓謝目標男子受重傷，送往屯門醫院救治，其餘3名傷勢較輕則送博愛醫院治療，經治療後，26歲姓曾男子稍後亦轉送屯門醫院留醫，姓卓司機(26歲)與姓陳(26歲)乘客則在博愛接受治理。警方翻查附近屋苑天眼追緝4南亞兇徒歸案，案件暫列傷人及縱火，交由元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/photo/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170302073144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170302073144&h=59052e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉事2輛私家車燒毀。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/photo/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_03b.jpg?20170302073144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20170302073144&h=d8204bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中一名傷者(黑衣)在醫院治理後由一名友人陪同返現場助查。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/photo/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_04b.jpg?20170302073144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20170302073144&h=e9387cc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉事2輛私家車焚毀。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/photo/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_05b.jpg?20170302073144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20170302073144&h=681d19ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兇徒私家車嚴重焚毀。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/photo/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_06b.jpg?20170302073144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20170302073144&h=3003b0c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場遺下一件外套及一攤血漬。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/photo/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_07b.jpg?20170302073144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_07b.jpg%3F20170302073144&h=b126d5e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批探員到場調查。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/photo/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_08b.jpg?20170302073144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_08b.jpg%3F20170302073144&h=5233de28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車廂坐椅滿布血漬。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/photo/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_09b.jpg?20170302073144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_09b.jpg%3F20170302073144&h=d316bb0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場檢獲一把刀。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/photo/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_10b.jpg?20170302073144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_10b.jpg%3F20170302073144&h=25b57298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玻璃窗金屬框刀痕纍纍。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/photo/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_11b.jpg?20170302073144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_11b.jpg%3F20170302073144&h=a49017bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防到場將火救熄。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/photo/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_12b.jpg?20170302073144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_12b.jpg%3F20170302073144&h=fc8ebe97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附近屋苑外牆裝有「天眼」。(郭垂垂攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/photo/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_13b.jpg?20170302073144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001_13b.jpg%3F20170302073144&h=7dabdbb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170302%2Fbkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001.html&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3bec3008\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170302/bkn-20170302013921415-0302_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid